OKAY KIDDOS LISTEN UP ( @Kunio )
First of all
The default font size is 12px
Changing it to 12px will do nothing
Secondly read the wiki ffs
The correct syntax is "font-size: 12px;"
Thirdly you can't modify the CSS of other elements within a custom game CSS file you have to inject the style properties in javascript
Fourthly
If you want to change styles internally to a label
You either apply the style to the label
eg <Label style="font-size: 48px;" text="Test" />
Or you add html to the label
Eg <Label html="true" text="white <a style="color: red;"> red </a>" />
